a CSS Single- / Multiline Style Switch for Sublime Text 2.
Based on  http://www.sublimetext.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=2237

##Installation##
1. Install in your Packages Folder
2. add 
  { "keys": ["ctrl+shift+j"], "command": "toggle_single_line_css" }
  to your user-shortcut file. 

*I am not a python programmer. But it's working ;)
Feel free to fork and modify!*




